stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle

    Idle: No active execution
    Idle: Last terminal RunSnapshot remains visible

    Initializing: RunCoordinatorActor and RuntimeManager starting
    Initializing: Runtime preflight and backend allocation

    Running: Active stage execution
    Running: StageRuntimeStatus and StageRuntimeUpdate fresh

    Completed: Linear stage plan finished successfully
    Completed: StageOutcome, artifacts, and RunSummary persisted

    Stopped: Run explicitly stopped by user or driver
    Stopped: Final snapshot captures partial results

    Failed: Runtime exception or preflight error
    Failed: Final snapshot captures error_message and traceback

    Idle --> Initializing: RunService.start_run()
    Initializing --> Running: RuntimeProxy ready
    Initializing --> Failed: Initialization error

    Running --> Completed: summary stage finished
    Running --> Stopped: stop_run()
    Running --> Failed: stage failure
